column1: Future Awareness - Awareness of global agricultural challenges
column2: Perceived Individual Efficiency - Belief in personal impact on sustainability
column3: Perceived Collective Efficiency - Belief in societal changes for sustainability
column4: Advocacy and Career Intentions - Interest in sustainability careers
column5: Tech Orientation - Trust in food production technology
column6: Unwillingness to Change - Resistance to dietary changes

column8: Social Support - Influence of peers on food choices
column10: Belief About Consequences - Impact of food choices on environment & health
column11: Emotions - Satisfaction and guilt related to sustainable food choices
column12: Food Preparation Skills - Ability to cook sustainable meals
column13: Green Purchase Intention - Commitment to buying sustainable food
